<h1 class="mar-b-xs">Head tags</h1>
<h2 class="txt-gray-5 mar-t-none">Special tags for branding, SEO, and PWA purposes</h2>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<p class="mar-t-none pad-all-lg txt-center">Look at your browser tab and favorites page, home screen icon, search engine results, and more to see how these tags are working for this site.<br>Your app would simply replace these values with assets for your app.</p>
